ELECTION TO DEFER
My election relates to each separate 12,125 common stock share tranche awarded to me under the Arbitron Inc. 1999 Stock Incentive Plan (the "") as restricted stock pursuant to the Restricted Stock Agreement (the "") between Arbitron Inc. (the "") and me, effective March 1, 2006, that is scheduled to vest on each of December 31, 2007, December 31, 2008 and December 31, 2009 (the ""). The Restricted Stock I elect to defer, upon vesting, will be converted into deferred stock units, and any such deferred stock units will be documented pursuant to a Deferred Stock Unit Agreement between the Corporation and me (the "Agreement"). This election does not relate to the 12,125 shares of restricted stock awarded to me pursuant to the Agreement that are scheduled to vest on December 31, 2006.
