Although the vote is non-binding, the Board of Directors values the opinion of our stockholders.  In light of the voting results on this proposal, the Board has determined that the Company will hold the advisory vote on executive compensation annually until the next stockholder vote on the frequency of holding an advisory vote on executive compensation.
